questiontext.text: List the last names of employee and the budget of their projects whose title is equal to the 'Hellion' and budget is greater than 12000, an order by title

question.answer: SELECT t1.budget,t0.last_name FROM employee AS t0 JOIN project AS t1 ON t0.project=t1.id WHERE t1.title = 'Hellion' AND t1.budget > 12000 ORDER BY t1.title

questiontext.text: List the last names of employee and the name of their departments whose city follows this expression A?ticus Minor where ? is any character and name contains a, an order by city

question.answer: SELECT t1.name,t0.last_name FROM employee AS t0 JOIN department AS t1 ON t0.department=t1.id WHERE t1.city LIKE 'A_ticus Minor' AND t1.name LIKE '%a%' ORDER BY t1.city

questiontext.text: List the salarys of employee and the city of their departments whose name is equal to the 'Production' and city is equal to the 'Goldilocks', an order by name

question.answer: SELECT t1.city,t0.salary FROM employee AS t0 JOIN department AS t1 ON t0.department=t1.id WHERE t1.name = 'Production' AND t1.city = 'Goldilocks' ORDER BY t1.name
